MESSAGE.value: Added njk template code to hopefully include the css files in the navbar.
Added css and js to templateFormats
Added my custom styles to the head.njk file. Site doesn't appear to be reading style.css but reads the other css files fine.
Moved nav bar to base file, wasn't working properly in the navbar component file. Seems to be working now that it's in base. Added the parallax header to the home page.
Added images to img folder in assets.
Finally figured out that images are served from static/img and that files uploaded through the CMS live in that directory. Awesome.

Created about.njk
Added CSS to make nav bar visible on pages other than home.

Added permalink to about header.
Updated contact form component
Fixed about page front matter. Added Services page.
Moved images to static/img and changed filepaths to the correct one.
Updated about page and services page.
